wiki.content:
"Not Gonna Get Us" (translated from "Нас Не Догонят") is the second single from t.A.T.u.'s debut English album 200 km/h in the Wrong Lane and was released in mid-2003. This was also to be the last song taken from that album in the UK, where it reached #7 on the singles chart.
